---
// WSIB and Safety Compliance Section - Enhanced from Dry Main
---

<section class="py-16 bg-navy-900 text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase">
          WSIB-Cleared Professional Teams
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Full safety compliance with WSIB clearance certificates, OHSA protocols, 
          and $5 million liability insurance for your complete protection
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- WSIB Certificate Display -->
      <div class="bg-white text-slate-900 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              WSIB Clearance Certificate
            </h3>
            
            <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-2 border-green-300 p-4 rounded mb-4">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-cyan-700 mb-2">Active Status Verified</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Account #: Available upon request</li>
                <li>✓ Coverage: Full workplace safety insurance</li>
                <li>✓ Status: Clear - No outstanding claims</li>
                <li>✓ Renewal: Annually maintained</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
              WSIB clearance certificates provided for every project. This ensures you're 
              protected from any workplace injury liability on your property.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1a1 1 0 002 0V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zM4 4h3a3 3 0 006 0h3a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2zm2.5 7a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3zm2.45 4a2.5 2.5 0 10-4.9 0h4.9zM12 9a1 1 0 100 2h3a1 1 0 100-2h-3zm-1 4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 110 2h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Liability Insurance
            </h3>
            
            <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-2 border-blue-300 p-4 rounded mb-4">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-cyan-700 mb-2">$5 Million Coverage</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ General liability: $5,000,000</li>
                <li>✓ Property damage coverage</li>
                <li>✓ Completed operations coverage</li>
                <li>✓ Certificate available upon request</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
              Comprehensive insurance coverage protects your property and investment 
              throughout the entire project and warranty period.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety Compliance Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 uppercase">OHSA Compliance</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Occupational Health & Safety Act compliant
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Daily safety meetings and hazard assessments
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Proper trenching and shoring procedures
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Fall protection for elevated work
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 uppercase">IHSA Training</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Infrastructure Health & Safety certified
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Working at Heights certification
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Confined space entry training
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              First aid certified personnel on site
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 uppercase">Safety Equipment</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Personal protective equipment (PPE)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Gas detection monitors
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Trench boxes and shoring systems
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">✓</span>
              Emergency response equipment
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Documentation Promise -->
      <div class="bg-amber-500 text-black p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase">Safety Documentation Provided</h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-lg">Before Project Start:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>WSIB clearance certificate</strong> - Confirms coverage</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Insurance certificate</strong> - $5M liability proof</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Safety plan</strong> - Site-specific procedures</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Team certifications</strong> - Training records</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-lg">After Project Completion:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>WSIB final clearance</strong> - No claims confirmation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Safety compliance report</strong> - Full documentation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Incident report</strong> - Zero incidents confirmation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-700 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Warranty documents</strong> - Coverage confirmation</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-black/10 rounded">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold">
            Your Protection is Our Priority: Every crew member is background-checked, 
            safety-trained, and committed to protecting your property throughout the project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <p class="text-xl mb-6">
          Work with Toronto's safest waterproofing contractor - 
          Zero workplace incidents in 25+ years
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/free-inspection" class="px-8 py-4 bg-amber-500 text-black font-bold text-lg hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors uppercase">
            Schedule Safe Installation
          </a>
          <a href="tel:437-545-0067" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors uppercase">
            Call: 437-545-0067
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>